\newlabel{fig:intro}{{1}{3}{Overview of the proposed knowledge-based robotic system with uncertainty-aware planning. The system maintains a belief over possible worlds and updates it based on observations. If the uncertainty exceeds a threshold, the system selectively queries the user to resolve ambiguity. Otherwise, it continues autonomous planning and execution.\relax }{figure.caption.2}{}}
